<%= email_greeting(@user) %>,

please use the following PIN to log in to vutuv:

  <%= @pin %>

Thanks for using vutuv! If you like our service, feel free to share us
with your friends!

<%= render "_signature_en.text" %>

PS: The PIN expires after 30 minutes. You can always get a new one at
<%= @url %>login

<%= render "_footer.text" %>
